OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy but mild, dry at first
OL,6,Fthen outbreaks of rain, heavy at times
OL,7,Fin the south, spreads north from mid-
OL,8,Fmorning. Becoming drier during the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy with rain in the west
OL,12,Fduring the evening. This rain becomes
OL,13,Fheavy at times from late evening. A
OL,14,Fmild and windy night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,17,Fbecoming dry from late morning with
OL,18,Fincreasing sunny spells during the
OL,19,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
